ZIPPING FIles
"zip myzip file1 file2 file3"

UNZIPPING FILES
unzip myzip.zip

TAKING OWNERSHIP
sudo chown -R bitnami:daemon /opt/bitnami/apps/joomla/htdocs/
sudo chown -R bitnami:daemon /opt/bitnami/apps/joomla/logs
sudo chown -R bitnami:daemon /opt/bitnami/apps/joomla/tmp/
sudo find  /opt/bitnami/apps/joomla/htdocs/ -type d -exec chmod 0775 {} \;
sudo find  /opt/bitnami/apps/joomla/htdocs/ -type f -exec chmod 0664 {} \;
sudo find  /opt/bitnami/apps/joomla/logs -type d -exec chmod 0775 {} \;
sudo find  /opt/bitnami/apps/joomla/logs -type f -exec chmod 0664 {} \;
sudo find  /opt/bitnami/apps/joomla/tmp -type d -exec chmod 0775 {} \;
sudo find  /opt/bitnami/apps/joomla/tmp -type f -exec chmod 0664 {} \;

Removing Directory without prompt
rm -rf dirname

Removing directory with prompts
rm -r dirname
